      <Description>The SC2 experiment has both science and engineering applications.  The electrostatic analyzers measure ions and electrons with energies from a few 10's of eV to ~20 keV, perpendicular to the spin axis.  SC2 also measures 20 keV ions with a temporal resolution of 250 msec for He and the CNO group (&gt;150keV/AMU) and one sec for protons.</Description>
